description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ready for the recognition&lt;em&gt;and rewards you deserve?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/em&gt; We don’t just talk about putting employees first. We know that Priory wouldn’t exist without their combined energy, expertise and effort. So we invest heavily in training, provide first-class support, promote collaborative teamwork and give everyone on our team the opportunities and resources to achieve their full potential. &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Heathfield is a Neuro Rehabilitation Service in Broad Oak, East Sussex which provides specialist nursing care, rehabilitation and support for individuals with neurological conditions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nursing and therapy programs are tailored for each individual and goals are developed in conjunction with their families to best reflect aspiration. Individuals are supported to take part in activities they enjoy, including sensory experiences, and families are encouraged to be involved through regular review meetings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Registered Nurse you will undertake and manage direct patient care, having participated fully in the assessment, planning and evaluation of care needs. Undertake the delivery of care, including individual and group sessions, to agreed quality standards as prescribed by internal procedures and health legislation. We are looking for keen and resourceful Registered Nurses to support our Clinical Team, in this role you&#39;ll be working both days and nights.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What we’d like from you:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;RMNor RGNQualified&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NMC (Nursing &amp; Midwifery Council Registered)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fine tuned decision making skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent organisational capability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexibility and strong “can do” attitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quality orientation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What we’d like to give you:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A competitive salary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhanced disclosure cost coverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive induction and commitment to ongoing training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;33 days annual leave inclusive of bank holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Online benefits and cashback rewards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cycle to work scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Just drive scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SMART Pension option&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;£5,000 Welcome Bonus paid over 3 years&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
